children.text: Enough Said spoken word series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on January 16, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by bill bissett and Sharon H. Nelson. Open mic/supporting performances by Scott Duncan, Halina Berger, Justin McGrail, and more.
